{
  "id": "adv_main_01_10_09",
  "title": "星見編2章43話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "医師",
      "speakerNameEn": "Doctor",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……なるほど。心臓の導き、ですか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Her heart led her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "医師",
      "speakerNameEn": "Doctor",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "不思議なこともあるものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The world is full of mysteries‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。さくらと出会った時、まるで麻奈が\n導いてくれたように思えて……それだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. When I met Sakura‚ it almost felt like Mana\nhad guided her to me… That’s all I wanted to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.297076611641126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（あえて、『麻奈』という名前を強調して先生を見る）\n（先生は観念したように俺の目を見た）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I emphasize the name “Mana” and look at the doctor.)\n(And he gives me a knowing look.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.592244974772136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "医師",
      "speakerNameEn": "Doctor",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……さくらちゃんにはそのことを言わないように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Be sure not to tell any of that to Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.592244974772136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "医師",
      "speakerNameEn": "Doctor",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私からの話は以上です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s all I have to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.35891164143881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 31.69224497477214
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 31.69224497477214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの？　暗い顔して\n何かあった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong? You’re frowning.\nDid something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.99224497477213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 36.458911641438824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……もし、さっきの会話を聞いていたなら）\n（こんなに平然とはしていられないか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(If she had listened in on my conversation with the doctor‚)\n(she wouldn’t be acting so normal now.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.39224497477213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 41.992244974772134
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……\n入ってくるなって言っておいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a relief…\nI’m glad I told you not to follow me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.658911641438806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "何が？\n……あ、さくらちゃんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?\nOh‚ it’s Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 49.458911641438775
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、先生とのお話、終わりました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Did you finish talking to the doctor?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 233.33333333333428,
          "startTime": 49.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、グランプリ、出ても問題ないそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. He said there shouldn’t be a problem with you being in the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.95891164143881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 57.958911641438775
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？　良かったぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? What great news!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.95891164143881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 61.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、少し待っててもらっていいですか？\n私も検査、もうすぐ終わりだと思うので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ could you wait here just a minute?\nI’m about to finish my exam.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.62063504854838,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6753.968381881712,
          "startTime": 68.35396838188171
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 69.68730171521509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　何？\nどうかした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What is it?\nWhat’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 74.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（言う訳にはいかない。さくらにも、麻奈にも）\n（何より、もし琴乃が知ったらどう思うだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(There’s no way I can tell her. Not Sakura or Mana either.)\n(Most importantly‚ I have no idea how Kotono would react if she knew.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 81.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（姉の歌声を持つ少女。その心臓が姉のものだと知れば）\n（ショックは大きい……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(If she knew that the girl who sings with her sister’s voice has her sister’s heart…)\n(It would shock her deeply.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらに特別な感情を抱かずにはいられないだろう）\n（さくらだって琴乃に罪悪感を抱くかもしれないな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She wouldn’t be able to not have special feelings for Sakura.)\n(And even Sakura might feel guilt towards Kotono.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 96.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "ほっとした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you relieved?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 98.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、何もなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That Sakura’s health is okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 100.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　あ、まあね\nこれで何の不安もなく、グランプリに挑める",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Oh… yeah.\nNow we can enter the Grand Prix without any worries.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 107.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "勝てる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think they can win?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "簡単じゃないだろうな\nけど、ここを目指して頑張ってきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It certainly won’t be easy.\nBut we’ve all worked so hard for this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 111.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "結果に関係なく、全力でステージで歌うみんなを\n見ることが出来たら、俺は幸せだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Win or lose‚ if I just get to see them on stage‚\nsinging their hearts out‚ I’ll be happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 121.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_09-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……そうだね\n私も、幸せだよ。きっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… Yeah‚ you will.\nAnd I’ll be happy‚ too. I know it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "03-3d",
      "startTime": 128.66666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
